data.description: What a wonderful ranch home! Enter through the front into the lovely 3-season room with brand new vinyl windows. Enjoy many days sitting in this peaceful space. The sq ft of this room is not included in the total sq ft of the house. This is bonus space! The windows all open and there is a ceiling fan for your comfort. The living room and dining room are open to each other by an arch way trimmed in oak woodwork. The baseboards are all wide oak. The kitchen features a range, built in microwave, and lg spice rack, garbage disposal, & ref. The first floor also offers 2 bedrooms with original woodwork and a full bath with a tub/shower surround and pedestal sink. This home features beautiful oak woodwork and solid oak front door! There is lots of space in the basement ready to finish for more living space, plus 2 rooms for storage (make sure to see how nice the room under the porch is). The back yard is completely fenced in with wood privacy fence for plenty of summer fun! Updates and features include all vinyl window, new furnace in 21, HWT 20, range & built in microwave 23. Please see list of all updates in the supplements. Call today for your private viewing!
